        "type": "path",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"One Action\" aria-label=\"One Action\">1</span></p><p><em>You intimidatingly press your opponent’s defenses— and their nerves—hoping to expose a fatal gap.</em></p><p>Spend 2 focus to make a melee weapon attack against a target’s Cognitive defense. On a hit, your target also loses one <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"One Action\" aria-label=\"One Action\">r</span> and loses focus equal to your ranks in <strong>Intimidation</strong>. On a graze, they lose half as much focus (rounded up) and don’t lose <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"One Action\" aria-label=\"One Action\">r</span>.</p><p>You can spend <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" style=\"color:#98a4f5\" data-tooltip=\"Opportunity\" aria-label=\"Opportunity\">O</span> from this test to gain <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"One Action\" aria-label=\"One Action\">2</span>, which you can use only to @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.Da4Xj4WnVbtHMH7k]{Strike} or activate a stance.</p>",
            "chat": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"One Action\" aria-label=\"One Action\">1</span></p><p>Spend 2 focus to make a melee weapon attack vs. Cognitive. On a hit, your target loses <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"One Action\" aria-label=\"One Action\">r</span> and loses focus equal to your ranks in <strong>Intimidation</strong>. On a graze, they lose half as much focus.</p>",
            "short": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"One Action\" aria-label=\"One Action\">1</span></p><p>Spend 2 focus to make a melee weapon attack against a target’s Cognitive defense. On a hit, your target also loses one <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"One Action\" aria-label=\"One Action\">r</span> and loses focus equal to your ranks in <strong>Intimidation</strong>. On a graze, they lose half as much focus (rounded up) and don’t lose <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"One Action\" aria-label=\"One Action\">r</span>.</p><p>You can spend <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" style=\"color:#98a4f5\" data-tooltip=\"Opportunity\" aria-label=\"Opportunity\">O</span> from this test to gain <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"One Action\" aria-label=\"One Action\">2</span>, which you can use only to @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.Da4Xj4WnVbtHMH7k]{Strike} or activate a stance.</p>"
